div
    h1 {{question.question}}
    div([hidden]="responses && responses.length")
        | 0 answers.
    div(*ngFor='let response of responses')
        div
            b {{response.firstname}}
            p(style='margin-top: 0') {{response.response}}
    hr
    label(for='firstname') Ton pseudo lapin:
    input(id="firstname" type='text', name='firstname', [(ngModel)]='newAnswer.firstname')
    br
    label(for='email') Ton email:
    input(id="email" type='text', name='email', [(ngModel)]='newAnswer.email')
    br
    label(for='newAnswer') Ta réponse mec:
    textarea(id="newAnswer" cols='30', rows='10', name='newAnswer', [(ngModel)]='newAnswer.response')
    button((click)='addResponse()') Submit
div([hidden]="!errorMessage || !errorMessage.length")
    | {{errorMessage}}